<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Welcome to <?= clubName ?></title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: #f6f6f6;
      }
      .container {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 20px auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        padding: 20px;
        border: 1px solid #dddddd;
      }
      .header {
        text-align: center;
        padding-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .content {
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.5;
        color: #333333;
      }
      .list {
        margin-left: 20px;
        padding-left: 20px;
      }
      .payment-box {
        border: 1px solid #eeeeee;
        background: #fafafa;
        padding: 14px 16px;
        margin: 16px 0;
      }
      .payment-box p {
        margin: 6px 0;
      }
      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #777777;
        margin-top: 30px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <img
          src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/e1isev/CCCC/refs/heads/main/CCCC_Logo.png"
          alt="Logo"
          style="max-width: 200px; height: auto;"
        />
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <p>Dear <?= firstName ?>,</p>

        <p>
          Welcome and thank you for joining <?= clubName ?>. We are excited to have you on board.
          We have registered your email address as <strong><?= email ?></strong> in our system.
        </p>

        <p>Please find below the details regarding your membership:</p>
        <ul class="list">
          <li>A once-a-year membership fee of <strong>$<?= membershipFee ?></strong> applies.</li>
          <li>Membership lasts one year from the date payment is received.</li>
          <li>Membership includes unlimited car applications during the membership period.</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="payment-box">
          <p><strong>Payment details</strong></p>
          <p>Account name: <?= bankAccountName ?></p>
          <p>BSB: <?= bankBsb ?></p>
          <p>Account number: <?= bankAccountNumber ?></p>
        </div>

        <p>
          If you have any questions or need assistance, please do not hesitate to get in touch.
        </p>

        <p>Best regards,</p>
        <p><?= clubName ?></p>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; <?= currentYear ?> <?= clubName ?>. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
